title: Neal Brennan 😑🙅🏻‍♂️
description:
Justin talks to comedian Neal Brennan (co-creator of Chappelle’s Show, 3 Mics) in front of an audience for his first-ever live show, and they talk about why ten kids is too many for a family.

Special thanks to Sonos for hosting us. And check out Neal's new podcast "How Neal Feel" https://www.nealbrennan.com/podcasts/how-neal-feel
